VALUES(4,'An insiders bike tour of Tulum','We will start our day by visiting the Mayan ruins of Tulum, early before the crowds. We will travel through different ecosystems such as the beach road, forest trails and some hidden places. We will see the local authenticity, the best spots and far from massive tourism.','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549414279-d6799fcf2279?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1074&q=80','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518105515732-8df2a35c0c56?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80',30,30,false,'Av. Coba Mza 05-Lote 01','Tulum','Quintana Roo','77760','Mexico',true,false,6,'spring','Sightseeing'),
  (5,'Scenic Hike up Hanauma Bay','A short easy hike up the Hanauma Bay for an amazing 3 in 1 view. Next, lets find the hidden lava tube at the beach surrounded by volcanic walls which are very unique. Then, you will be taken to a secret spot and enjoy a combination scenic view. After that, we will picnic our lunch at the beautiful Waimanalo beach. Finally, you can take a dip in the turquoise water or just relax on a comfortable beach blanket that I provide in the shade.','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586477572631-c0663f9a03dd?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580432958970-ec46508dcfb4?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1169&q=80','30','30',false,'265 Kaelepulu Dr','Kailua','Hawaii','96734','United States',true,false,20,'summer','Sightseeing'),
  (6, 'Sailboat Tour','After a very nice welcome drink and everybody on board. We will sail along the beautiful coastline as the sun descends on the horizon, you will enjoy and see pink and purple hues take center stage and light up the sky.','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540946485063-a40da27545f8?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466786694873-154f8914bc02?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80',80,80,true,'Av. Tulum Mza 4 Lt 5','Tulum','Quintana Roo','77780','Mexico', true,false,10,'summer','Sightseeing');

